data.description: Welcome home to this remarkable Lakeland home with 4 BRMs/3 Baths, and a bonus room that can serve as a 5th bedroom which offers plenty of space and flexibility for your family's needs. The floorpan on the lower level was designed with a potential for an in-law wing. The proximity to the Lake District and the 25-minute drive to Blue Oval City make this home an appealing choice for those who value both nature and urban amenities. Notable features: new roof, new tankless water heater and windows.
